question: What is the name of the administrative center of Cēsu novads (Cēsis county) in Latvia?
asked_question_translated: Mis on Cēsu novads (Cēsise maakonna) halduskeskuse nimi Lätis?
answer: Cēsu novads'i halduskeskus Lätis on Cēsise linn.
answer_translated_eng: The administrative centre of Cēsu novads in Latvia is the city of Cēsis.
